        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4061805" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9201432055389286544">I really wanted to love this book, mostly because it’s the first novel written by an elderly woman, and I love the idea of late-life accomplishment. And I did like it, but I didn’t love it. The story was reasonably interesting and the writing style was okay, but neither really wowed me. But I know some readers think this is a wonderful book and I did enjoy it so I wouldn’t want to dissuade anybody from reading it.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


